Package: SNPstats
Type: Package
Title: SNP Statistics for Genetic Epidemiology
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2026-04-10
Authors@R: person("Victor", "Moreno", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "v.moreno@iconcologia.net")
Description: Performs single-SNP and haplotype association analyses for
    genetic epidemiology studies. Computes allele and genotype frequencies,
    Hardy-Weinberg equilibrium tests, SNP-response association under five
    genetic models (codominant, dominant, recessive, overdominant,
    log-additive), linkage disequilibrium, and haplotype analysis.
    Based on the SNPstats web tool (Catalan Institute of Oncology).
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
